{"tid":386352,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打可以分享下啲好文章","createTime":"2017-09-03T19:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T17:17:40.000Z","uid":105220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01ee01d1e766303537f97a857571a5049bfe12ef","tid":386352,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:49:14.000Z","msg":"又開學<br />\n<br />\n真係好掛住以前中學中文堂 <br />\n<br />\n可以自己靜靜地睇下書入面啲課文 真係覺得好開心 <br />\n<br />\n人大左 唔好話睇書賞文 打機都冇時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家分享下你覺得好睇 深刻嘅 文章 (唔係中學課文都得)<br />\n<br />\n一齊回味下閱讀文章嘅樂趣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4614c91de0f9a84bdcf41be90b78f055972f2d0f","tid":386352,"uid":86886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:53:58.000Z","msg":"睇下小說囉 都係文章黎"},{"pid":"2a3eda5bf574f37ee1d104a3b2eadff984b393eb","tid":386352,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"陶傑"},{"pid":"4519190e4c7032df0e05834583366d19e873c730","tid":386352,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下小說囉 都係文章黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太長喇 冇時間"},{"pid":"0d598e4373575bea2c6b3976ce28a001b67176ed","tid":386352,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3425a7a4d7e26a1f80186ed70f6ecbc27098b56f","tid":386352,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"可以追我Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fafb51420411b696320b76c25d8b24ebdce879c","tid":386352,"uid":105220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以追我Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgm